** Word wrapping
please wrap text around when in text-modes. Also enable flyspell to catch nasty writing errors.
#+BEGIN_SRC emacs-lisp
  (dolist (hook '(text-mode-hook))
    (add-hook hook (lambda ()
                     (flyspell-mode 1)
                     (visual-line-mode  1))))
#+END_SRC
